{"tid":2378041,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一套高質tvb膠劇","createTime":"2021-01-24T06:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T07:35:04.000Z","uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ec865948fef08babdc79755abe9e9b352c7028b2","tid":2378041,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"《桌球天王》<br />\n<br />\n由鄭少秋領銜主演、09年的《桌球天王》卻被網頁視作世紀膠劇，當中一招白波撞足七個咕𠱸邊的「七重天」，也被指毫不科學。法國花式桌球手Florian Kohler曾於2016年在fb分享該劇片段，並寫下「當中國人製作有關桌球的電影&hellip;&hellip;」，至今引來222萬人次觀看。有網民詳細介紹劇集是來自香港，他回覆指「這是很好的故事，但劇情好瘋狂。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《情迷黑森林》<br />\n<br />\n在《情迷黑森林》中飾演蛋糕高手的馬德鐘就有一對「冷凍之手」。因為他雙手溫度先天就比常人低，朱古力在他手上不會太快融掉，所以在整朱古力造型時便會比其他人多了時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《戀愛自由式》<br />\n<br />\n當年唐寧飾演的Rain常常在比賽的緊張關頭就使出破冰轉身，就是到達池邊時，一個轉身，身邊的水好像凝結成冰，然後唐寧再破冰而出，展現驚人的爆發力，為隊伍扭轉劣勢。除了破冰轉身外，劇集還有「片石轉身」，「擾流泳法 」，「磁浮泳法」等，真是花招百出！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《超時空男臣》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vzqp0UC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzqp0UC.png&h=c1a8fa28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b03811e75b2f193154fb8000c8e7de0600ed8a11","tid":2378041,"uid":69866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/venomtrickshotsofficial/videos/1074177446007244/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvenomtrickshotsofficial%2Fvideos%2F1074177446007244%2F&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=8f9f561f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/venomtrickshotsofficial/videos/1074177446007244/</a>"},{"pid":"b420f09097e73a41d14061251c5cb5359ed22d27","tid":2378041,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"叛逃"},{"pid":"b23929afe8f2361f186aa6b1818333830377c0f9","tid":2378041,"uid":33445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"TVB 劇我淨係會推薦人睇大東瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829347e8d33081a4c5c7e49aefc3953d48ce72bb","tid":2378041,"uid":56111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b23929afe8f2361f186aa6b1818333830377c0f9","tid":2378041,"uid":33445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"TVB 劇我淨係會推薦人睇大東瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:58:12.000Z","msg":"十兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f023ac7d88463c81d26d528e508467ddb505673","tid":2378041,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"美味天王都無？"},{"pid":"fe5da3c4a150d4e39a6bf6a5205895fed589f66e","tid":2378041,"uid":375949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:34:17.000Z","msg":"神探哥倫布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e2ed693de72d38328725ead57fd58853acfef3","tid":2378041,"uid":247085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b23929afe8f2361f186aa6b1818333830377c0f9","tid":2378041,"uid":33445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"TVB 劇我淨係會推薦人睇大東瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"大冬瓜 鳩毛開叉"}]}